name: StandUpFacts
0:
”Alexa, ask stand up facts”
”Alexa, ask stand up facts for comedian facts”
”Alexa, ask stand up facts for george carlin facts”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: stand up facts
des: This skill is triggered by utterances such as "stand up facts" or "comedian facts". This then prompts the user on whether they would like to receive their fact or quit. If they choose to receive their fact then one is randomly chosen from a pool of 15. Based off of the space geek template.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
